1220
01:09:48.084 --> 01:09:51.905
But if you talk to any big pharma, especially with TCEs, what they want to

1221
01:09:51.945 --> 01:09:55.864
see is single agent activity. So what we're trying to do

1222
01:09:56.504 --> 01:09:59.344
to go about that is incorporate another domain there.

1223
01:09:59.824 --> 01:10:02.624
If you go back, I put in red costimulation.

1224
01:10:02.724 --> 01:10:06.364
So when you look at the interface between antigen

1225
01:10:06.384 --> 01:10:09.464
presenting cells and T cells, you have your CD3

1226
01:10:11.244 --> 01:10:15.124
zeta signaling as your signal one, and you have a plethora of choices on

1227
01:10:15.144 --> 01:10:19.124
what your signal two can be. Taking a cue from the CAR

