01:10:22.804 --> 01:10:25.824
generation T cell engagers CD28 or

1230
01:10:25.884 --> 01:10:29.684
4-1BB, and there's also OX40. But there's a few reasons

1231
01:10:29.724 --> 01:10:32.084
why we didn't choose to use any of those.

