01:10:32.244 --> 01:10:36.144
4-1BB and OX40, they're not constitutively expressed

1233
01:10:36.184 --> 01:10:39.744
on T cells. They're inducibly expressed, so they're not there

1234
01:10:39.804 --> 01:10:41.604
initially when you give the T cell engagers.

